messageBody:
I've got some good news and some bad news. The bad news is I will
not be attending XP/Agile Universe. I am moving back to the Bay Area
the week before, and things are just to crazy.

But have no fear, the good news is J. B. Rainsberger will be running
the JUnit BOF!

There is even more good news, it's not to late to get the early bird
rate but you do have to hurry as the deadline is June 1st!

There are tons of tutorials and workshops
http://www.xpuniverse.com/schedule/schedule.

Featured speakers include: Kent Beck, Barry Boehm, Alistair Cockburn,
Martin Fowler, Richard P. Gabriel, Watts S. Humphrey, Ron Jeffries,
Robert C. Martin, and Dave West.

Erik Meade
http://junit.org
